---
title: Beef Bolognese Pasta Bake with Mixed Salad
description: Pasta bakes are a classic for a reason, and they’re even better when loaded with veggies, topped with herby tomato sauce and finished with a golden cheesy topping. Time to get back to the basics and dig into this baked delight!

*Unfortunately, this week's courgette was in short supply, so we've replaced it with baby spinach leaves. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
